153
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:55,900
Takže chápu jeho vášeň pro CTF.

154
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:58,090
Ne, ne.

155
00:09:58,090 --> 00:10:00,420
- Jeho proslov o odchodu do důchodu? <br>- Ano.

156
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:05,480
